title: Hunted Channel 4 Dispatches Documentary 480p 30fps
description:

Provided here since it should be available to everybody around the world and not just the United Kingdom.


Source: http://www.channel4.com/programmes/dispatches/4od#3651833
Resolution: 852x480
Encoding: H.264 - MPEG-4 AVC
FPS: 30 (only 25 from source)
Rip method: Screencapture

Audio: Stereo
Encoding: MPEG AAC (mp4a)
